               <msContents>
                  <summary>Antiphonary for the Whole Year, ድጓ፡, with musical notation.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="98v" facs="003">Fols 1r–98v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3178Deggwa">Dǝggʷā</title></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="43v">Fols 1r–43v</locus><title>For the season of Yoḥannǝs and for the Sabbaths and for Lent</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ[፡] ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ጸሐፍነ፡ ድጓ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ መስወልድዋእቱ፡ (sic) ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ምድር፡ በምልአ፡ ወእግዚአብሔር፡ ነግሠ፡ ወይትባረክ፡ አርያም፡ ወመዝሙር፡ አምላኪየ፡ ወእእዝል (sic) ወዘይእዜ፡ ማኅሌተ፡ ወስብሐተ[፡]ነግህ በ፪ ብፁዕ፡ አንተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ዘሀለወከ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="44v" to="45v" facs="047">Fols 44v–45v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3178Deggwa#Haleta">Dǝggʷā, Table of
                                                  melodic variations for the Hallelujah (same as
                                                  https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1110Anqasa)</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="47r" to="72v" facs="049">Fols 47r–72v</locus><title>For the Season of Tǝnśa’e (Easter) and the Rainy Season</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ምል፡ ዮም፡ ፍሥሐ፡ ኮነ፡ በሰንበተ፡ ክርስቲያን እስመ፡ ተንሥአ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እሙ፡ (sic) ክርስቶስ፡ እሙታን፡ ቀደሳ፡ ወአክበራ፡ እምኵሎን፡ መዋዕል፡ አልዓላ፡ (አልዓላ)፡ አማን፡ ተንሥአ፡ እምነ፡ ሙታን።</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="73r" to="95v" facs="075">Fols 73r–95v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3186Meeraf">Mǝʿrāf</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ምዕራፍ፡ እምዮሐንስ፡ እስከ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ቅዱስ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቅዱስ፡ ኃያል፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሕያው፡ ዘኢይመውት፡ ዘተወልደ፡ እማርያም፡ እምቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ ተሣሃለነ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ምድር፡ በምልዓ፡ ይቤ ዮ፡ ዓለም፡ ወኵ፡ ለልየ፤ ርኢኩ፡ ወውእቱ፡ በባሕር፡ ሣረራ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ዝማሬ፡ እምዮሐንስ፡ እስከ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ሖረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ እምገሊላ፡ ኀበ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ከመ፡ (እምገሊላ፡ ኀበ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ከመ) ያጥምቆ፡ በፈለገ፡ ዮርዳኖስ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
